source code here is typed in according to:
http://typesafe.com/resources/getting-started/tutorials/getting-started-with-akka-scala.html

to run in command line:

1. compile
scalac -cp /home/yuqi/.ivy2/cache/com.typesafe.akka/akka-actor/jars/akka-actor-2.0.jar src/main/scala/home/learning/akka/pi/Pi.scala 

2. run
java -cp .:/usr/share/java/scala-library.jar:/home/yuqi/.ivy2/cache/com.typesafe.akka/akka-actor/jars/akka-actor-2.0.jar home.learning.akka.pi.Pi

